"# RouterOS 7.5
# software id = 
#
/interface bridge
add name=loopback
/interface ethernet
set [ find default-name=ether1 ] advertise="10M-half,10M-full,100M-half,100M-f\
    ull,1000M-half,1000M-full,10000M-full,2500M-full,5000M-full" \
    disable-running-check=no
/interface wireguard
add listen-port=63665 mtu=1420 name=wireguard1
/interface lte apn
set [ find default=yes ] ip-type=ipv4 use-network-apn=no
/interface wireless security-profiles
set [ find default=yes ] supplicant-identity=MikroTik
/port
set 0 name=serial0
set 1 name=serial1
set 2 name=serial2
set 3 name=serial3
/routing ospf instance
add disabled=no name=ospf-instance-2 router-id=12.12.12.12
/routing ospf area
add disabled=no instance=ospf-instance-2 name=Backbone
/user group
set full policy="local,telnet,ssh,ftp,reboot,read,write,policy,test,winbox,pas\
    sword,web,sniff,sensitive,api,romon,dude,rest-api"
/ip neighbor discovery-settings
set discover-interface-list=all lldp-med-net-policy-vlan=1
/ip settings
set max-neighbor-entries=8192
/ipv6 settings
set max-neighbor-entries=8192
/interface ovpn-server server
set auth=sha1,md5
/interface wireguard peers
add allowed-address=0.0.0.0/0 endpoint-address=51.250.103.248 endpoint-port=\
    63665 interface=wireguard1 persistent-keepalive=25s public-key=\
    "+xokQjKM8wXNvflurwqHWQvbD56caH1kMLABBuQws3M="
/ip address
add address=10.66.66.4/24 interface=wireguard1 network=10.66.66.0
add address=10.0.0.3 disabled=yes interface=ether1 network=10.0.0.3
/ip dhcp-client
add !dhcp-options interface=ether1
/ip firewall filter
add action=accept chain=output disabled=yes protocol=ospf
add action=accept chain=input disabled=yes protocol=ospf
/ip firewall service-port
set rtsp disabled=no
/routing ospf interface-template
add area=Backbone disabled=no networks=192.168.0.0/24
add area=Backbone disabled=no networks=192.168.0.0/24
add area=Backbone disabled=no networks=192.168.0.0/24
add area=Backbone disabled=no networks=192.168.0.0/24
/system ntp client
set enabled=yes
/system ntp client servers
add address=0.ru.pool.ntp.org# nov/13/2022 20:56:15 by RouterOS 7.5
